Usage: knbn [option] [arguments]

Tasks
  add, -a, --add [column] [description]
    Add a task to a column
  ls, -l, --list [column],...
    List tasks in selected columns
  ls, -l, --list
    List all tasks
  mv, -m, --move [old column] [new column] [task id]
    Move a task
  rm, -d, --remove [column] [task id]
    Delete a task from a column
  wipe, -w, --wipe [column]
    Delete all tasks in a column

Notes
  nt, -n, --note [column] [task id] [description]
    Add a note to a task
  rmnt, -r, --remove-note [column] [task id] [line offset]
    Delete a note from a task

Backup and restore
  backup, -b, --backup [column] [backup location]
    Backup the kanban board
  restore, -R, --restore [backup location]
    Restore from backup

Other
  uninstall, -u, --uninstall
    Uninstall knbnBrd
  license, -L, --license
    Print license
  notice, -N, --notice
    Print GPLv3 notice and contact information
  help, -h, --help
    Print this
  examples, -e, --examples
    Print examples
  --create-dir
    Create knbn board directory

